        "category": "classfeature",
        "description": {
            "value": "<p>The life essence shed from blood empowers your chalice. If you or an ally within 30 feet takes piercing or slashing damage from a foe's critical hit or takes persistent bleed damage, @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.Drink from the Chalice]{Drinking from the Chalice} before the end of your next turn grants that injured creature greater restoration to make up for its lost vitality.</p>\n<p>On a sip, the temporary Hit Points granted to the creature increase to twice your level. When drained, the chalice heals the creature 5 Hit Points for each level you have.</p>"
        },
